//Degeneration - I describe

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Spine MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Degeneration' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' radio button is enabled and selected by default
And 'I know' radio button is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And multiple choice localizer is enabled

And 'Bone bridges' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ankylosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Osteophytes, anterior' checkbox is enabled

And 'Erosions' checkbox is enabled
And 'Joint space narrowing' checkbox is enabled
And 'Vacuum phenomenon' checkbox is enabled

And 'Subchondral cysts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral sclerosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fat deposition' checkbox is enabled

And 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Ankylosis' checkbox
Then 'Total' radio button is enabled
And 'Partial' radio button is enabled
and 'Periarticular' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Subchondral sclerosis' checkbox
Then 'Close to the joint space' radio button is enabled
And '> 5 mm distance from joint space' radio button is enabled

When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu
Then 'Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown menu
Then 'Secondary' checkbox is enabled
